dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially.   Includes 6 views of cities, coat-of-arms of Silesia, coat-of-arms of Poland, and 8 illustrations showing typical dress of residents of Poland, Silesia, and Danzig.   "Are to be sold by Thomas Bassett in Fleet Street and Richard Chiswell in St. Pauls Churchyard."   Text on verso: "The description of Poland."
